{
  "stem": "24515.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To go on the Kindertransport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had three or four days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time things were so urgent, that there was hardly any discussion.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can tell you the last thing my father said to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can tell you that in a minute, but first I want you to understand what the children's transports were.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The British government had said they would take 10,000 children, selected by some German Jewish organization, and the government would be the sponsor, as it were, would look after them until they could be on their own.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As far as, to my knowledge, the only government action taken by a civilized-- ugh, civilized-- country, and for [INAUDIBLE] almost like winning the Irish sweepstakes, I was chosen for this.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Most of the people chosen were the children of Jews who'd come from Poland, whom the Germans had taken, and tried to push into Poland.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Poles had tried to hold them, and they were lying in the [INAUDIBLE] area, being filed on by both sides.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were children [? left on that. ?] Some of them came on these children's transports.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But my suspicion is that I was chosen because I was closer-- becoming closer, and closer to 16.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Nazis, in a very organized German fashion, tended to leave people under 16 alone, and over 16 put them in the concentration, and slave labor camps.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway, I was chosen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I came home one day from school, I forget, a Wednesday or-- I'm not quite sure.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my aunt said, mother had just called.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was to go home immediately, I was leaving for England on Tuesday.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know we went around a little bit.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
